  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "羊脂球",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23228652_3_6398-6698",
          "range": "6398-6698",
          "rangeStart": 6398,
          "rangeEnd": 6698,
          "markText": "那个女的呢，是一个被人们称为婊子的主儿；她由于过早发福而闻名，得了一个名副其实的绰号叫“羊脂球”。她个头儿矮胖，浑身圆滚滚的，肥得油脂流溢，连一根根手指也是肉鼓鼓的，只有每个骨节周围才细一圈，皮肤紧绷而发亮，像一串短香肠。她的胸脯丰满挺拔，在连衣裙里高高耸起。她皮肤细嫩，明艳照人，叫人看着就怦然心动，其顾客着实不少。她的脸蛋像一只红苹果，又像一朵含苞欲放的牡丹花，脸蛋上部，两只美丽而乌黑的眼睛闪闪发亮，四周围着一圈又长又浓的睫毛，而睫毛又倒映在眼波里；她脸蛋的下部则是一张媚人的小嘴，两排细牙洁白明亮，嘴唇柔美湿润，简直就是专为接吻而造设的。 \n    据说，她还有许许多多难以言传的媚人妙处。 ",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1674289229,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-01-21 16:20:29",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23228652&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6398&rangeEnd=6698",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78832260716270ec7889504?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6398&rangeEnd=6698"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23228652_3_1172-1196",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1172-1196",
      "markText": "等待所引起的焦虑不安，反而使人盼望敌军早日进驻。",
      "totalCount": 486,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23228652&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1172&rangeEnd=1196",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78832260716270ec7889504?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1172&rangeEnd=1196"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23228652_3_30134-30182",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "30134-30182",
      "markText": "羊脂球一直在饮泣；夜色茫茫，有时在歌曲的两个节拍之间，传出她未能忍住的一声呜咽。 注释",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23228652&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=30134&rangeEnd=30182",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78832260716270ec7889504?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=30134&rangeEnd=30182"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23228652_3_23428-23483",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "23428-23483",
      "markText": "听来听去，你就会相信，女人活在世上，其唯一的使命，就是永无止境地奉献自己的肉体，没完没了地听任大兵丘八的玩弄。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23228652&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=23428&rangeEnd=23483",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78832260716270ec7889504?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=23428&rangeEnd=23483"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23228652_3_6858-6958",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6858-6958",
      "markText": "但不一会儿，那三位女士又开始交谈，有这妓女在场，她们突然亲近起来，甚至可以说成为了亲密的朋友。面对这个无耻的卖淫女，她们似乎觉得必须拧成一股绳，以显示有夫之妇的尊严，因为合法的婚姻从来都鄙视淫行苟合。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23228652&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6858&rangeEnd=6958",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78832260716270ec7889504?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6858&rangeEnd=6958"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23228652_13_3375-3426",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3375-3426",
      "markText": "“因为……因为……他对你说‘你可爱的小脚不冷吗？’……从来没有人对我这么说过，从来没有……从来没有！”",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23228652&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3375&rangeEnd=3426",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78832260716270ec7889504?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3375&rangeEnd=3426"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23228652_3_9926-9993",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9926-9993",
      "markText": "最后，还是伯爵当机立断，打破僵局，他转过头去，对着那怯生生的胖姐，摆出一副高不可攀的贵族派头，说道：“好吧，夫人，我们领情接受邀请。”",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23228652&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9926&rangeEnd=9993",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78832260716270ec7889504?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9926&rangeEnd=9993"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23228652_3_24438-24502",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "24438-24502",
      "markText": "她俩就这样一问一答地交谈着，共同判断上帝的意愿，预测上帝的决定，玩弄上帝于股掌，强使上帝为一些与己无关的事情操心劳神，承当责任。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23228652&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=24438&rangeEnd=24502",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/78832260716270ec7889504?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=24438&rangeEnd=24502"
    },
